rows.label: qst660101_msg0003
rows.name:
Tora see unfamiliar object,
right over there...

rows.label: qst660101_msg0004
rows.name:
D'you think that's the mysterious
light Zuo mentioned...?

rows.label: qst660101_msg0005
rows.name: It wasn't here before, that's for sure...

rows.label: qst660101_msg0006
rows.name: No, I imagine I'd have remembered.

rows.label: qst660101_msg0007
rows.name:
But what is it...?
Tora-senses are tingling...

rows.label: qst660101_msg0008
rows.name:
If you're so curious, Tora,
why don't you go check it out?

rows.label: qst660101_msg0010
rows.name:
N-no, Tora believe discretion is better
part of valor. Curiosity kills more Nopon
than Aligo... Maybe Boss check?

rows.label: qst660101_msg0012
rows.name:
Though I'd be lying if I said I wasn't
curious myself...

rows.label: qst660101_msg0013
rows.name:
Just like with salvaging, if you don't
take chances, you'll never make it
to the good stuff!

rows.label: qst660101_msg0014
rows.name: Right on, Rex! Go do your thing.

rows.label: qst660101_msg0016
rows.name: Just please don't do anything reckless...
